&lt;li&gt;Implement internal corrosion monitoring programs and develop corrective actions to mitigate corrosion threats.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support field technicians with advanced troubleshooting of rectifiers, bonds, areas of inadequate CP, or DC and AC interference issues.&lt;/li&gt;
