&lt;li&gt;AMPP Cathodic Protection Technician (CP2) or Internal Corrosion for Pipeline 2.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Successful completion of applicable Operator Qualification training.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Working knowledge of computer software packages and equipment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Working knowledge of mathematics and electricity.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Working knowledge of CFR 49 Part 192 and/or Part 195.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong organizational, communication, and collaboration skills.&lt;/li&gt;
