&lt;li&gt;Experience conducting threat, risk, and vulnerability assessments.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong incident management, investigation, and crisis response experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience managing third-party security providers and security technologies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent leadership, communication, and stakeholder management skills.&lt;/li&gt;
