&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;Join our Qrew!&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;As a key member of the EQT Commodities Team, the Principal Originator will lead strategic origination and business development efforts across the Midwest natural gas market, focused on creating value through portfolio optimization, structured transactions, and innovative commercial solutions. This role is responsible for identifying and executing opportunities that enhance the value of EQT’s transportation and storage portfolio, including releasing existing capacity, securing new capacity in emerging markets, and developing new products and service offerings that meet customer needs.&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Principal Origination responsibilities include but are not limited to:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;Develop value-add strategies around our existing firm transportation &amp;amp; storage portfolio. This may involve releasing existing capacity and/or adding new capacity in new regions.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;Structure &amp;amp; execute complex transactions that create value for both EQT and our customers.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;Business Development of new trading counterparties pipelines and storage operators.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;Develop new product/service offerings.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;Able to perform basic analysis and financial modeling to assess the value-add of a particular proposal.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
