&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Operate EQT’s SCADA and other relevant systems and data sources; including extracting data trends used for analysis&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
